title: Yeah Yeah Yeahs at Coachella 2009
description:
Yeah Yeah Yeahs perform at the 2009 Coachella Music Festival in Indio California on Sunday April 19, 2009

This is nearly their entire set. Only the last song is missing.

Audio extracted from my MiniDV video footage of their set and encoded into 320kbps mp3s using Adobe Audition.

To preview what the audio sounds like and to see video of the Yeah Yeah Yeahs set go to my YouTube page by visiting youtubeDOTcom/magmazing


Tracks:
01. Runaway
02. Dull Life
03. Gold Lion
04. Honeybear
05. Black Tongue
06. Human Fly
07. Zero
08. Cheated Hearts
09. Skeletons
10. Soft Shock
11. Maps
12. Heads Will Roll

The last song in their set "Y Control" is missing because my camcorder ran out of tape.

I share this recording simply a fan of the Yeah Yeah Yeahs and do not make a cent from its distribution.

If you burn this to CD be sure to burn it in such a way that there is no delay between tracks. I have split the recording in such a way that it should play seamlessly as if it's one continuous track

This recording brought to you by Magmazing Music and KickStart Multimedia
